item.title: Kirkistown R2
item.description: {{ more }} Another brutal night, head wind at the top of the circuit heading to the start finish straight. At least this time I was able to stay in a group all night, just not the right group.

item.title: Kirkistown R1
item.description: {{ more }} First race since BC, dropped on the first lap head wind and very fast start. Kept on going and was caught by the main group after a lap and finished comfortably in the group.
